OL,6,GTelescopes are fun, obviously more an
OL,7,Gevening / night thing but pending the
OL,8,Gweather on Friday the moon should be
OL,9,Gamazing around dusk and on Saturday
OL,10,Gthe moon and Venus should both be
OL,11,Gvisible through dusk and until around
OL,12,G10pm. Maybe someone will bring a solar
OL,13,Gscope for sun viewing too? Super happy
OL,14,Gfor folk to join this village ♥️🔭
OL,15,GYou're welcome to bring a scope, do
OL,16,Gnot touch other people's scopes
OL,17,Gwithout consent, but you can go down a
OL,18,Grabbit hole of visual and photographic
OL,19,Gastronomy.
